After studying tripadvisor for some time we decided to make the best of our single-night stay in Vancouver by booking the Granville Island Hotel and we were not let down.	My wife and i keep coming back, and every time we stay we think how lucky we are to have found this hotel.	We often visit Vancouver to see family, and decided to stay someplace different.	We had been to Vancouver Island two times in the past and have always wanted to stay at this hotel but couldn't get in.	We try to stay at the Granville Island Hotel whenever we travel to Vancouver.